{
  "texts": [
    "The instructor evaluated the relevance and comprehensiveness of the AIenhanced content, looking for evidence of improvement in how well the materials supported the learning outcomes.",
    "The initial prompt inputted into ChatGPT aimed to establish five distinct learning outcomes.",
    "Along with a detailed course description, there was an emphasis on integrating content from both the sixth and seventh editions of the Project Management Body of Knowledge (PMBOK) book (Project Management Institute 2017, 2021).",
    "Additionally, the user inquired about any additional information necessary to enhance the results for the course learning outcomes, as depicted in Fig. 3.",
    "ChatGPT requested details on areas such as \"Depth of Coverage,\" \"Assessment Method,\" \"Course Duration & Intensity,\" \"Target Audience,\" \"Prerequisites,\" and \"Key Textbooks and Resources.\""
  ]
}